"and 255."
msgstr ""
"<sgmltag class=\"starttag\">green</sgmltag>, <sgmltag class=\"endtag"
"\">green</sgmltag>: 색상의 녹색 성분입니다. 0부터 255까지입니다."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<sgmltag class=\"starttag\">blue</sgmltag> and <sgmltag class=\"endtag"
"\">blue</sgmltag>: blue component of the color. Valid values are between 0 "
"and 255."
